Run <Obey$Dir>.!Boot

If "<GCC$Dir>" = "" Then Error 0 !GCC must have been seen by the filer

If "<Clang$Path>" = "" Then Set Run$Path <Run$Path>,Clang:
Set ClangGCCBin$Path <GCC$Dir>.
Set Clang$Path <Clang$Dir>.bin.

| The same compiler binary is used for both C and C++. The file extension
| is used to determine which mode to run it in. For convenience, provide
| a clang++ alias.
Set Alias$clang++ clang %*1

Set UnixEnv$clang$sfix "cc:cxx:cpp:c++:C:i:c:m:h:hh:s:S:ll:o:y:tcc:cmhg"
